iris1=iris %>%
  mutate(Petalarea=Petal.Length*Petal.Width,Sepalarea=Sepal.Length*Sepal.Width)
ggplot(iris1,aes(x=Sepal.Length,y=Sepal.Width,color=Species,size=Petalarea))+
         geom_point()
